CPL = cpl.Coupler(1000000000.0, 50, modelmappath)
res = CPL.design(_maxiter=0)
assert round(1000000.0 * res.x[0], 3) == 0.015
assert round(res.x[1], 3) == 2
assert round(1000000.0 * res.x[2], 3) == 1156.925
assert round(1000000.0 * res.x[3], 3) == 0.5
CPL.print(res)
res = CPL.design(_maxiter=1)
